    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Creamy Brie and Mushroom Risotto. The dish belongs to the Italian home-cooking register: straightforward, ingredient-led, calm at the hob. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Stock kept warm beside you, rice toasted, wine in, ladle by ladle until the grains are soft with a bite at the centre. No need to stir constantly — gently, often."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What you need"
          }
        ]
